a huge teacher for me

00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:36.474
and I'm really excited to
for him to come to Google.

00:00:36.474 --> 00:00:38.140
But yeah, without any
other further ado,

00:00:38.140 --> 00:00:39.973
I'd love to introduce
you to Michael Nagler.

00:00:39.973 --> 00:00:43.540
