00:08:36.100 --> 00:08:41.110
You might call it
Western civilization 2.0.

00:08:41.110 --> 00:08:43.419
What's happening
is we are actually

00:08:43.419 --> 00:08:46.480
in a very awkward situation.

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:50.500
This is why there is so much
violence and disruption going

00:08:50.500 --> 00:08:52.120
on in our world.

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:56.470
It's not because we have only
a thin veneer of morality.

00:08:56.470 --> 00:08:57.955
Stephanie and I,
and Metta Center,

00:08:57.955 --> 00:09:02.530
are up in smoke country
and the north counties

00:09:02.530 --> 00:09:06.670
and the outpouring of
support and volunteers

00:09:06.670 --> 00:09:09.280
has been absolutely
overwhelming.

00:09:09.280 --> 00:09:11.420
We got a call a couple
of days ago from somebody

00:09:11.420 --> 00:09:16.240
who wanted to donate clothing
to us because she had tried

00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:17.980
to donate them to
all the centers

00:09:17.980 --> 00:09:22.090
that had evacuees in them and
they weren't taking any more.

00:09:22.090 --> 00:09:24.670
They had mountains and
mountains of clothing.

00:09:24.670 --> 00:09:28.320
In fact, Lou, who is
doing the film with us,

00:09:28.320 --> 00:09:30.970
spent the whole day sorting
through mountains of clothing

00:09:30.970 --> 00:09:34.340
so that evacuees or anybody
else could come and get them.

00:09:34.340 --> 00:09:37.450
So it was this huge
outpouring of compassion

00:09:37.450 --> 00:09:38.980
that was immediately
touched when

00:09:38.980 --> 00:09:44.200
our community, our
neighborhood, was in crisis.

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:46.960
But there was a
study, or an article,

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:50.890
recently about the fact
that we are experiencing

00:09:50.890 --> 00:09:53.230
an epidemic of depression.

00:09:53.230 --> 00:09:55.230
We've got our share
of epidemics going on.

00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:57.220
We've got an opioid epidemic.

00:09:57.220 --> 00:10:00.950
There's an epidemic of suicides
among military personnel.

00:10:00.950 --> 00:10:03.160
Might get back to
that in a little bit.

00:10:03.160 --> 00:10:05.560
And there's an
epidemic of depression.

00:10:05.560 --> 00:10:08.660
All of those things are symptoms
of this great awkwardness

00:10:08.660 --> 00:10:11.210
I'm going to say a
word about in a minute.

00:10:11.210 --> 00:10:17.020
And this author said that
that is a misdiagnosis.

00:10:17.020 --> 00:10:21.670
It's not really depression
that we're dealing with.

00:10:21.670 --> 00:10:24.746
What we're dealing
with is demoralization.

00:10:24.746 --> 00:10:30.100
There's demoralization because--
this is where the New Story

00:10:30.100 --> 00:10:32.060
comes in--

00:10:32.060 --> 00:10:38.780
we're operating with a model of
reality in our mind which is--

00:10:38.780 --> 00:10:41.020
the three things to be
said about it, aside

00:10:41.020 --> 00:10:43.840
from the fact that it's been
there for a couple hundred

00:10:43.840 --> 00:10:50.290
years now, it is demoralizing,
it is extremely harmful,

00:10:50.290 --> 00:10:52.360
and it's dead wrong.

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:55.990
And that model-- which I'm
going to show you some examples

00:10:55.990 --> 00:10:58.240
of how it's shared everywhere--

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:01.270
is that we're all
material beings

00:11:01.270 --> 00:11:06.490
and we're determined by
mindless forces, everything

00:11:06.490 --> 00:11:12.430
from genes to cosmic rays
to hormones and so forth.

00:11:12.430 --> 00:11:15.700
We have no control over
our destiny, right?

00:11:15.700 --> 00:11:19.900
So we have to respond to every
advertisement and signal that

00:11:19.900 --> 00:11:21.920
comes down the line.

00:11:21.920 --> 00:11:25.930
And we basically have no
meaning on this planet.

00:11:25.930 --> 00:11:28.780
Now, you may not believe
that, and I congratulate you

00:11:28.780 --> 00:11:31.060
for seeing through the fog.

00:11:31.060 --> 00:11:34.240
But the fact is that
this is the model which

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:37.700
is operational for most people.

00:11:37.700 --> 00:11:40.210
You do not have to prove it.

00:11:40.210 --> 00:11:44.990
If you assume it, you can
simply refer back to it,

00:11:44.990 --> 00:11:47.800
and people are supposed
to follow along with you.

00:11:47.800 --> 00:11:50.230
So the next thing I'd
like to show you--

00:11:50.230 --> 00:11:53.410
which may need some help
from Maria, not sure--

00:11:53.410 --> 00:11:59.410
is an animation that we've done
to illustrate this shift that's

00:11:59.410 --> 00:12:01.280
going on to the New Story.

00:12:01.280 --> 00:12:04.360
And so in order to not
keep you in suspense--

00:12:04.360 --> 00:12:07.390
I can almost sense the
rising tension in the room--

00:12:07.390 --> 00:12:10.570
the New Story, as hinted
at by those scientists

00:12:10.570 --> 00:12:12.850
that you just saw
in the trailer--

00:12:12.850 --> 00:12:15.910
and we have several of
them in the finished film--

00:12:15.910 --> 00:12:20.280
is that in fact, we are
body, mind, and spirit.

00:12:20.280 --> 00:12:23.140
And just to paraphrase
the New Testament,

00:12:23.140 --> 00:12:24.460
we are body, mind, and spirit.

00:12:24.460 --> 00:12:28.660
All three of these, but
spirit is the most important.

00:12:28.660 --> 00:12:35.260
And we are deeply
interconnected with one another,

00:12:35.260 --> 00:12:40.840
