00:12:54.155 --> 00:12:57.450
You're telling them, oh, you're
so wonderful, you're so great,

00:12:57.450 --> 00:12:58.890
you're saving our country.

00:12:58.890 --> 00:13:00.710
Well, the President
doesn't say that,

00:13:00.710 --> 00:13:05.040
but the culture as a
whole is saying that.

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:08.240
Look, there's lots of seats
here if you'd like to come in.

00:13:08.240 --> 00:13:09.740
There's enough
violence in the world

00:13:09.740 --> 00:13:11.781
