from this country, from a group
called Christian Peacemaker

00:13:54.560 --> 00:14:00.050
Teams, which is part of this
new institution that's sprung up

00:14:00.050 --> 00:14:04.510
called Unarmed Civilian
Peacekeeping or protection,

00:14:04.510 --> 00:14:06.890
Unarmed Civilian Protection.

00:14:06.890 --> 00:14:08.690
This Kurdish
gentleman said, well,

00:14:08.690 --> 00:14:11.780
we're going to try and do it
from here out with nonviolence.

00:14:11.780 --> 00:14:14.480
And the person from
Christian Peacemaker Teams

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:17.960
said, you know, you can
do that if you want to,

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:23.210
but it's very difficult,
which is true.

00:14:23.210 --> 00:14:27.200
It can be dangerous,
which is an exaggeration,

00:14:27.200 --> 00:14:30.710
and it takes more time,
which is not true at all,

00:14:30.710 --> 00:14:32.060
we just found out.

00:14:32.060 --> 00:14:34.250
And he said, I know
all of those things,

00:14:34.250 --> 00:14:37.850
but you don't lose your
soul in the process.

00:14:37.850 --> 00:14:40.170
You don't lose your
humanity in the process.

00:14:40.170 --> 00:14:43.250
So I like to present this
as a stark contrast which

00:14:43.250 --> 00:14:47.420
illustrates the impact of
operating on the wrong story

00:14:47.420 --> 00:14:49.670
and letting it draw
you into action

00:14:49.670 --> 00:14:53.090
and operating on the New Story,
despite the fact that nobody

00:14:53.090 --> 00:14:56.190
knows what the heck
you're trying to do.

00:14:56.190 --> 00:15:01.010
So we feel that the
development of the New Story

00:15:01.010 --> 00:15:02.690
and the development
of nonviolence

00:15:02.690 --> 00:15:07.670
go hand-in-hand, like opposite
sides of the same coin.

00:15:07.670 --> 00:15:10.680
The New Story will
never be complete.

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:14.780
We feel-- we being
basically me and Stephanie--

00:15:14.780 --> 00:15:18.890
we feel, at Metta, that the New
Story will never be complete

00:15:18.890 --> 00:15:22.640
until it makes this discovery
that this film is driving

00:15:22.640 --> 00:15:27.680
at that the capacity
to be nonviolent

00:15:27.680 --> 00:15:30.710
is the core of our
human identity.

00:15:30.710 --> 00:15:32.810
So when you are
nonviolent, you feel

00:15:32.810 --> 00:15:35.570
that you are closer
to fulfilling yourself

00:15:35.570 --> 00:15:36.370
as a human being.

00:15:36.370 --> 00:15:41.330
That's why the subtitle of
the working title of the film

00:15:41.330 --> 00:15:44.900
is nonviolence
and human destiny.

00:15:44.900 --> 00:15:47.150
And on the other
hand, nonviolence,

00:15:47.150 --> 00:15:49.310
as I'm going to be
showing in a bit,

00:15:49.310 --> 00:15:52.310
is very difficult
to grasp if you've

00:15:52.310 --> 00:15:56.780
got that old story, that
old paradigm, or model

00:15:56.780 --> 00:15:58.200
in your mind.

00:15:58.200 --> 00:15:58.700
OK.

00:15:58.700 --> 00:16:01.674
So here is the animation
that we created.

00:16:01.674 --> 00:16:02.340
