00:20:17.260 --> 00:20:21.310
at the university in 1970,
handed around these little

00:20:21.310 --> 00:20:25.240
mimeograph-- you
don't remember those--

00:20:25.240 --> 00:20:29.260
sheets talking about
the prevailing paradigm,

00:20:29.260 --> 00:20:32.170
the dominance paradigm, a.k.a.

00:20:32.170 --> 00:20:36.160
the Old Story, and the
emerging paradigm, a.k.a.

00:20:36.160 --> 00:20:36.910
the New Story.

00:20:36.910 --> 00:20:39.730
But it still hasn't
emerged, despite the fact

00:20:39.730 --> 00:20:42.820
that we have this great
